    {8827,"Winter's Presents",-1,-22,{"emulator","wago"},"I hear Greatfather Winter - with the generous support of Smokywood Pastures - has put presents for everyone under the tree in Ironforge. I wish I could go, but I've got to look after the PX-238 Winter Wondervolt.$B$BBut you should definitely check it out. I'm sure Greatfather Winter has some presents with your name on them.",nil,{15732},nil,1,0,nil,"Speak with Greatfather Winter. He is located near the Smokywood Pastures vendor area in Ironforge.",8,nil,1101,nil,{13444}},
    {8828,"Winter's Presents",-1,-22,{"emulator","wago"},"I hear Great-father Winter - with the generous support of Smokywood Pastures - has put presents for everyone under the tree in Orgrimmar. I wish I could go, but I've got to look after the PX-238 Winter Wondervolt.$B$BBut you should definitely check it out. I'm sure Great-father Winter has some presents with your name on them.",nil,{15732},nil,1,0,nil,"Speak with Great-father Winter. He is located near the Smokywood Pastures vendor area in Orgrimmar.",8,nil,690,nil,{13445}},
    {8829,"The Ultimate Deception",60,1377,{"emulator"},"The Twilight's Hammer operates through innumerable layers of secrecy and deceit.  While their actions are carried out in our world, they are planned in a place we have not yet been able to reach.$B$BWe've come to believe that the stones the Twilight's Hammer uses to summon their superiors allow for two-way transportation.  To attempt to use them in this manner, we must replicate - to every last detail - a twilight emissary's robe.$B$BGather the necessary materials and bring them to Aurel Goldleaf, $N.",nil,nil,{{itemID=21515,count=1}},60,0,nil,"Bring a Skin of Shadow, 3 Frayed Abomination Stitchings and 1 Twilight Cultist Robe to Aurel Goldleaf at Cenarion Hold in Silithus.  You must also bring Logistics Task Briefing XI in order to complete this quest.",256,nil,nil,nil,{15282}},
