    {9188,"Craftsman's Writ - Brightcloth Pants",60,139,{"emulator"},"The bearer of this writ is entitled to payment in the form of an insignia of their choice upon completion of the contracted work order.$B$BWork Order TR-95:$B$B6 Brightcloth Pants.$B$BAll filled orders should be delivered to Packmaster Stonebruiser at Light's Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands.$B$BContract is null and void if tampered with or damaged.$B$B-Dispatch Commander Metz, The Argent Dawn",nil,nil,nil,55,0,nil,"Deliver 6 Brightcloth Pants and the Craftsman's Writ - Brightcloth Pants - to Packmaster Stonebruiser at Light's Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands.",64,nil,nil,nil,{16283}},
    {9189,"Delivery to the Sepulcher",15,130,{"emulator","wago"},"You have stirred the lady's heart, though it no longer beats.$B$BHowever, I have instructions that must be delivered to the Sepulcher in Silverpine Forest.  Advisor Sorrelon represents us to the Forsaken there.$B$BThe shortest route, barring the use of their flying bats, is to leave Undercity and take the road south.  Follow the signposts.  Finding the place shouldn't be difficult.  Brace yourself, though; the Sepulcher itself is a dilapidated crypt.$B$BThese Forsaken are certainly odd creatures.",nil,{16287},nil,15,350,nil,"Deliver the Sealed Sin'dorei Orders to Advisor Sorrelon at the Sepulcher in Silverpine Forest.",128,nil,690,nil,{16288}},
    {9190,"Craftsman's Writ - Runecloth Boots",60,139,{"emulator"},"The bearer of this writ is entitled to payment in the form of an insignia of their choice upon completion of the contracted work order.$B$BWork Order TR-635:$B$B8 Runecloth Boots.$B$BAll filled orders should be delivered to Packmaster Stonebruiser at Light's Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands.$B$BContract is null and void if tampered with or damaged.$B$B-Dispatch Commander Metz, The Argent Dawn",nil,nil,nil,55,0,nil,"Deliver 8 Runecloth Boots and the Craftsman's Writ - Runecloth Boots - to Packmaster Stonebruiser at Light's Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands.",64,nil,nil,nil,{16283}},
    {9191,"Craftsman's Writ - Runecloth Bag",60,139,{"emulator"},"The bearer of this writ is entitled to payment in the form of an insignia of their choice upon completion of the contracted work order.$B$BWork Order TR-9999:$B$B8 Runecloth Bags.$B$BAll filled orders should be delivered to Packmaster Stonebruiser at Light's Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands.$B$BContract is null and void if tampered with or damaged.$B$B-Dispatch Commander Metz, The Argent Dawn",nil,nil,nil,55,0,nil,"Deliver 8 Runecloth Bags and the Craftsman's Writ - Runecloth Bag - to Packmaster Stonebruiser at Light's Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands.",64,nil,nil,nil,{16283}},
    {9192,"Trouble at the Underlight Mines",14,3433,{"emulator","wago"},"The Underlight Mines to the southwest have been overrun by a clan of gnolls calling themselves the Blackpaw. I don't need to remind you how important those mines are to us as a strategic asset in our ongoing campaign here in the Ghostlands!$B$BTake the south road out of town and follow the fork to the right. Just past the ziggurat on the right there will be a short dirt path to the west. Follow it.$B$BThe ore must flow!",nil,{16251},nil,11,600,nil,"Slay 8 Blackpaw Gnolls, 6 Blackpaw Scavengers and 4 Blackpaw Shaman, and return to Deathstalker Maltendis at Tranquillien in the Ghostlands.",136,nil,690,nil,{16251}},
    {9193,"Investigate the Amani Catacombs",17,3433,{"emulator","wago"},"$C, our sources tell us that the trolls buried in the Amani Catacombs inside Sungraze Peak have been rising from the dead. Dame Auriferous would have you investigate these catacombs and put to the torch any of the unanimated remains you come across so as to prevent any more of these creatures from rising.$B$BThe fastest way there is to head north out of town and then take the first fork to the right. This will put you on the north side of the peak, so look to the south for the entrance.","Investigate the Amani Catacombs",{16289},nil,14,900,{"Mummified Troll Remains Burned"},"Investigate the Amani Catacombs and burn 10 Mummified Troll Remains, then return to Advisor Valwyn at Tranquillien in the Ghostlands.",132,nil,690,nil,{16289}},
    {9194,"Craftsman's Writ - Runecloth Robe",60,139,{"emulator"},"The bearer of this writ is entitled to payment in the form of an insignia of their choice upon completion of the contracted work order.$B$BWork Order TR-7229:$B$B8 Runecloth Robes.$B$BAll filled orders should be delivered to Packmaster Stonebruiser at Light's Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands.$B$BContract is null and void if tampered with or damaged.$B$B-Dispatch Commander Metz, The Argent Dawn",nil,nil,nil,55,0,nil,"Deliver 8 Runecloth Robes and the Craftsman's Writ - Runecloth Robe - to Packmaster Stonebruiser at Light's Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands.",64,nil,nil,nil,{16283}},
    {9195,"Craftsman's Writ - Goblin Sapper Charge",60,139,{"emulator"},"The bearer of this writ is entitled to payment in the form of an insignia of their choice upon completion of the contracted work order.$B$BWork Order EN-11:$B$B20 Goblin Sapper Charges.$B$BAll filled orders should be delivered to Packmaster Stonebruiser at Light's Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands.$B$BContract is null and void if tampered with or damaged.$B$B-Dispatch Commander Metz, The Argent Dawn",nil,nil,nil,55,0,nil,"Deliver 20 Goblin Sapper Charges and the Craftsman's Writ - Goblin Sapper Charge - to Packmaster Stonebruiser at Light's Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands.",64,nil,nil,nil,{16283}},
