    {12513,"Nice Hat...",68,2367,{"emulator","wago"},"My hat? Yes, it's an unusual style, I know, from far away... few tailors here know how to make them.$B$BWhen I was young and hot-blooded, I wore it as a standing challenge. Many came seeking to defeat me and win it for themselves... but no one ever did.$B$BAh, but those days are long past. I'm an old man, now: I drink, I fish, but I no longer duel.",nil,nil,{{itemID=38276,count=1}},66,0,nil,"Don Carlos has inadvertently challenged you to defeat his younger self in Old Hillsbrad. Afterwards, bring Don Carlos' Hat to him in Tanaris as proof.",256},
    {12515,"Nice Hat...",68,1941,{"emulator","wago"},"My hat? Yes, it's an unusual style, I know, from far away... few tailors here know how to make them.$B$BWhen I was young and hot-blooded, I wore it as a standing challenge. Many came seeking to defeat me and win it for themselves... but no one ever did.$B$BAh, but those days are long past. I'm an old man, now: I drink, I fish, but I no longer duel.",nil,{28126},{{itemID=38276,count=1}},66,0,nil,"Don Carlos has inadvertently challenged you to defeat his younger self in Old Hillsbrad. Afterwards, bring Don Carlos' Hat to him in Tanaris as proof.",128,nil,nil,nil,{28126}},
